My process making a set of paintings of Heart and Brain! 
This #CreatorChronicles video may be the last, I hope you have enjoyed them! If you'd like to continue to see extra content like this, you can support my work at patreon.com/theawkwardyeti

If you're interested in owning the original paintings, they will be for sale in the Art section at theAwkwardStore.com soon.

node.text: Just a casual #creatorchronicles update about beginning to learn 2 new instruments. I find switching to music is a great way to gain inspiration without leaving the creative space. Then I can come back to my regular work a little more refreshed. If you're a musician, let's see what you're up to lately! And if you're not, what are you listening to lately?
